PROBLEM:
#100 - sObject Type

Implement the method isTypeAccount(), which accepts a sObject as input and returns a 
true if type of input is Account object else it should return as false.

Given the following test code:
Account acc = new Account(name='Apple')
Boolean result = isTypeAccount(acc);
result should be equal to true

Hint 1:
Use instanceof method

-------------------------------
SOLUTION:

public Boolean isTypeAccount(sObject record)
{
    return record instanceof Account;
}